		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />As far as I can recall, there is still no clone that matches the NES. I don't know if and don't think any of them fix the sound duty cycle issues, and I don't know if any will work properly with the MMC5 or not. Clones just aren't worth it in my opinion. If you want something more compact maybe try a NES2/AV Famicom?

		

